<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Design Guide</title>

<style>
body {
  margin:0;
  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
  background:#f5f5f7;
  color:#1d1d1f;
}

.container {
  max-width:900px;
  margin:auto;
  padding:20px;
}

h1 {
  font-size:28px;
  margin-bottom:20px;
}

.section {
  background:white;
  border-radius:16px;
  padding:20px;
  margin-bottom:20px;
  box-shadow:0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
}

.slider {
  display:flex;
  overflow-x:auto;
  gap:10px;
  margin:15px 0;
}

.slider img {
  width:260px;
  height:260px;
  object-fit:cover;
  border-radius:12px;
  flex-shrink:0;
}

.prompt {
  background:#f2f2f2;
  padding:12px;
  border-radius:10px;
  font-size:14px;
  direction:ltr;
}
</style>

</head>

<body>
<div class="container">

<h1>Art Styles Guide</h1>

<!-- Surrealism -->
<div class="section">
<h2>Surrealism</h2>

<div class="slider">
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/d/dd/The_Persistence_of_Memory.jpg">
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/6/6d/Metamorphosis_of_Narcissus.jpg">
</div>

<div class="prompt">
Surrealism, dreamlike scene, symbolic imagery, irrational composition
</div>
</div>

<!-- Cubism -->
<div class="section">
<h2>Cubism</h2>

<div class="slider">
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/1/1c/Les_Demoiselles_d%27Avignon.jpg">
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/9/99/Pablo_Picasso%2C_1912%2C_Guitar.jpg">
</div>

<div class="prompt">
Cubism, fragmented geometry, multiple viewpoints, structured composition
</div>
</div>

<!-- Impressionism -->
<div class="section">
<h2>Impressionism</h2>

<div class="slider">
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/08/Claude_Monet_-_Water_Lilies_-_Google_Art_Project.jpg">
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3a/Claude_Monet_Impression_sunrise.jpg">
</div>

<div class="prompt">
Impressionism, loose brush strokes, light-driven colors, soft edges
</div>
</div>

<!-- Minimalism -->
<div class="section">
<h2>Minimalism</h2>

<div class="slider">
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/6a/Donald_Judd_untitled_1980.jpg">
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/0f/Minimalist_poster_design.jpg">
</div>

<div class="prompt">
Minimalism, very few elements, strong negative space, clean composition
</div>
</div>

<!-- Cyberpunk -->
<div class="section">
<h2>Cyberpunk</h2>

<div class="slider">
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/5f/Tokyo_Shibuya_night.jpg">
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3e/Hong_Kong_night_city.jpg">
</div>

<div class="prompt">
Cyberpunk, neon lighting, futuristic city, dark atmosphere, high contrast
</div>
</div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
